name: Salad Caprese
description: Sliced mozzarella. Sliced tomatoes. Sweet basil. Olive oil. Salt. That’s it.

name: Salad Niçoise
description: Tomatoes, hard-boiled eggs, Niçoise olives, anchovies, cucumber and olive oil. Many people also choose to include tuna.

name: Caesar Salad
description: Romaine lettuce, croutons, lemon juice, olive oil. Egg. Worcestershire sauce,  lemon juice, olive oil. Egg. Worcestershire sauce, anchovies, garlic, Dijon mustard, Parmesan cheese, and black pepper.

name: Club Sandwich
description: A hearty sandwich with layers of turkey, bacon, lettuce, tomato, and mayonnaise, typically served on toasted bread and cut into quarters, often with a side of pickles or chips.

name: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
description: A comfort food favorite made with slices of melty cheese sandwiched between buttered bread and grilled to golden perfection, often paired with a bowl of tomato soup.

name: Reuben Sandwich
description: A savory sandwich filled with corned beef, Swiss cheese, sauerkraut, and Russian dressing, grilled between slices of rye bread until warm and gooey.

name: Turkey and Avocado Sandwich
description: A fresh and flavorful combination of sliced turkey, creamy avocado, lettuce, tomato, and a touch of mayonnaise or mustard, served on whole grain bread.

name: Vanilla Bean Ice Cream
description: A classic and timeless flavor made with real vanilla beans, providing a rich and creamy texture with a smooth, aromatic vanilla taste.

name: Chocolate Fudge Brownie Ice Cream
description: Decadent chocolate ice cream swirled with gooey fudge and loaded with chunks of chewy brownie, perfect for chocolate lovers

name: Strawberry Cheesecake Ice Cream
description: Creamy cheesecake-flavored ice cream blended with luscious strawberry swirls and chunks of real cheesecake, creating a delightful dessert experience.

name: Strawberry Cheesecake Ice Cream
description: Creamy cheesecake-flavored ice cream blended with luscious strawberry swirls and chunks of real cheesecake, creating a delightful dessert experience.

name: Shrimp and Garlic Egg Roll
description: Succulent shrimp seasoned with garlic and mixed with cabbage and carrots, creating a flavorful and crispy egg roll

name: Beef and Broccoli Egg Roll
description: A hearty combination of tender beef strips and fresh broccoli florets, seasoned and wrapped in a crunchy egg roll wrapper.

name: BBQ Pulled Pork Egg Roll
description: Smoky pulled pork mixed with tangy barbecue sauce and slaw, wrapped in a golden, crunchy shell for a Southern-inspired treat.

name: Crab Rangoon Egg Roll
description: Creamy and savory crab Rangoon filling made with crab meat, cream cheese, and green onions, all wrapped in a crunchy egg roll skin.

name: Carrot Cake
description: A moist and spiced cake made with grated carrots, walnuts, and a hint of cinnamon. Typically layered and frosted with a rich cream cheese icing, adding a perfect balance of sweetness and tang.

name: Red Velvet Cake
description: A visually stunning cake with a vibrant red color and a subtle cocoa flavor, complemented by layers of creamy and tangy cream cheese frosting. A classic favorite for celebrations.

name: Victoria Sponge Cake
description: A classic British cake with two layers of light and airy sponge cake sandwiched together with a layer of strawberry or raspberry jam and a generous amount of whipped cream or buttercream.

name: Opera Cake
description: A French dessert made up of layers of almond sponge cake soaked in coffee syrup, layered with ganache and coffee buttercream, and topped with a chocolate glaze. It’s a sophisticated and richly flavored cake.

name: Mini Samosas
description: Small triangular pastries filled with a spicy mixture of potatoes, peas, and aromatic spices, then deep-fried until crisp and golden. Served with mint and tamarind chutneys.

name: Gourmet Stuffed Mushrooms
description: Succulent button mushrooms generously filled with a rich blend of creamy cheese, herbs, and breadcrumbs, then baked to golden perfection. A sophisticated appetizer for any occasion.

name: Cheese and Corn Croquettes
description: Delightfully crispy on the outside and creamy on the inside, these croquettes are made from a luscious mix of sweet corn, cheese, and herbs. Breaded and deep-fried to a golden hue.

name: Penne Arrabbiata
description: Penne pasta tossed in a spicy tomato sauce made with garlic, tomatoes, and red chili peppers, offering a bold and fiery flavor

name: Fettuccine Alfredo
description: Rich and creamy, this dish features fettuccine pasta coated in a sauce made from butter, heavy cream, and Parmesan cheese, often garnished with parsley.

name: Rigatoni alla Norma
description: Rigatoni pasta mixed with a flavorful tomato sauce, fried eggplant, garlic, and basil, topped with a generous amount of ricotta salata cheese.

name: Linguine
description: Long, flat pasta noodles, narrower than fettuccine but wider than spaghetti, commonly served with seafood-based sauces or pesto.

name: Fettuccine
description: Flat, wide noodles, similar to spaghetti but broader, often paired with creamy sauces or served in dishes like fettuccine Alfredo with Parmesan cheese and butter.

name: Udon
description: Thick, chewy Japanese wheat noodles, typically served in a savory broth or stir-fried with vegetables and protein, offering a hearty and comforting meal.

name: Vegetable Stir-Fry
description: A colorful medley of vegetables like broccoli, bell peppers, carrots, and snap peas stir-fried in a savory sauce made with soy sauce, garlic, ginger, and sesame oil.

name: Glass Noodles
description: Glass noodles, also known as cellophane noodles, are made from mung bean starch and are translucent.

name: Dan Dan Noodles
description: Dan Dan noodles are a classic Sichuan dish featuring spicy minced pork served over wheat noodles. The dish is known for its distinctive flavor, combining numbing Sichuan peppercorns with spicy chili oil.

name: Salad Caprese
description: Crisp romaine lettuce with Caesar dressing, croutons, and Parmesan cheese.

name: Greek Salad
description: Fresh cucumbers, tomatoes, red onions, olives, and feta cheese with a tangy vinaigrette.
